<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13049544/mountain-bar-2.jpg" alt="Apres" rel="838,360" /></p>
</div>
<p>It’s not all ski, ski, ski and with so many venues throwing a great party, it’d be a travesty not to give them a go! From dancing on tables (both inside and out), to enjoying a cool one in a hot-tub, or enjoying a great meal at an atmospheric restaurant in the middle of the deserted slopes, there really is something for every occasion.</p>
<p>Between us here at Inghams, we’ve covered a fair bit of ground, both on and off the slopes (for educational purposes of course) so we’ve put together some handy Insider's Guides for our favourite apres ski bars, drinks and dishes. Why not try and sample some for yourself?</p>
<p> </p>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13049542/mooserwirt.jpg" alt="Mooserwirt" width="490" height="276" rel="4800,2700" /><br /><span style="color: #023761; font-weight: bold;"><a data-udi="umb://document/c5916c331c6749bfb531802bd82b72b9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c5916c331c6749bfb531802bd82b72b9}" title="Insider's Guide: Top 12 Apres Ski Bars">Insider’s Guide: Top 10 Apres Ski Bars</a><a href="/{localLink:2ff87f97-1406-4899-8321-62705cd015d2}" title="Best Ski Resorts for Beginners"></a></span><br />We have devised a top 10 apres ski bars list because... you know... why not? We'll let you know where we think the hottest venues in the Alps are located. We'll also tell you why to head to them to get your apres fix and what you can expect from these cracking party spots. Shine up those dancing shoes!</p>
