<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13049252/drink.png" alt="Drink" width="490" height="280" rel="490,280" /><br /><span style="color: #023761; font-weight: bold;"><a data-udi="umb://document/8839cb283a0f4179a3c4c3b926cb5675" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8839cb283a0f4179a3c4c3b926cb5675}" title="Insider's Guide: Top 5 Apres Ski Drinks">Insider’s Guide: Top 5 Apres Ski Drinks</a> </span><br />Whether you're a complete beginner who wants to sample the world of skiing and snowboarding before you commit to a holiday to the Alps... or you simply can't get enough of your favourite sport, sometimes visiting a skiing and snowboarding centre here at home is the quick, fun fix you need.</p>
