  <shortDescription><![CDATA[<p>The art of apres ski remains a real cornerstone of the ski holiday and for many it's as important an element of the trip as the skiing itself.</p>
<p>So with that in mind, we've created an apres ski zone especially for you, giving you access to see what we recommend when it comes to this great tradition.</p>]]></shortDescription>
